What is Machine Learning?
Machine learning is an aspect of data science that deals with the automation of analytical model building.
Machine learning allows computers to find hidden insights without being explicitly programmed where to look.

Types
There are 3 main types of machine learning algorithms:
- Supervised learning
- Unsupervised learning
- Reinforcement learning

Uses
Fraud detection
Pricing models
Customer segmentation
Text-to-speech recognition
Recommendation engines
Email spam filtering etc
